⚠️ Common Mistakes
❌ Uploading the private key instead of the public key
❌ Committing SSH keys to GitHub
❌ Using an incorrect file path with the file() function
❌ Forgetting to initialize Terraform before planning
❌ Hardcoding environment-specific values instead of using variables

